high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the stool, then walk around the counter to the blue bin to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the tomato out of the blue bin.
Turn around and walk towards the counter, then turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge on the bottom shelf, then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and take out the tomato.
Walk over to where the microwave is on the counter.
Put the chilled tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the blue bin on the floor, to the left of the refrigerator.
Pick up the tomato that is inside the blue bin, on the floor.
Go to the front of the refrigerator on your right.
Place the tomato on the second shelf, between the bowl and the bread, in the refrigerator for a moment to let it chill, then remove the tomato from the refrigerator.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the microwave, on the counter to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the tomato on the plate that is inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Take a tomato from the bin
Put the tomato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave
